{"_total":124,"_totalPage":13,"_page":13,"posts":[{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/重新出发.json","date":1458002788000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"重新出发"},"title":"重新出发","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/重新出发/","content":"<p>当当读书提示我花了半个多月的时间阅读完了蔡崇达的首部作品–《皮囊》。事实上，我本来还想花更多的时间去慢慢阅读的，只不过今天没能收得住手，一下子就把剩下来的几篇文章给读完了。可惜的是这本书只有350页，而不是3500页。<br>"},{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/不合时宜.json","date":1458002732000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"不合时宜"},"title":"不合时宜","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/不合时宜/","content":"<p>站在山顶，看着脚下的繁华都市，大街小巷的车水马龙，听着这座城市跳动的脉搏，你能想到的是什么？<br>"},{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/老了也很美.json","date":1458002681000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"老了也很美"},"title":"老了，也很美","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/老了也很美/","content":"<ul>\n<li>此文献给《飞屋环游记》和《暗恋桃花源》</li>\n</ul>\n<p>久闻话剧《暗恋桃花源》大名，却始终没能一睹其风采，今天无意之间在偶像来了最后一期中，看到了其中的一个片段，汪涵不愧是博采众长，虽是话剧的处女秀，但表现出来的情绪透过冷冷的屏幕也感动着每一个人。<br>"},{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/黑暗面.json","date":1458002183000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"黑暗面"},"title":"黑暗面（死亡笔记&冰血暴S1&忠奸人）","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/黑暗面/","content":"<p>拖沓了近三周，终于在真正意义上看完了一部动漫——死亡笔记。第一次接触这部作品应该是在大学本科期间，当时同学推荐的是电影版本，看完之后只是觉得很新奇，果然日本的动漫总是会有一些很奇怪的想法，"}]}